            <h2>our history</h2>
            <p>
                For many years, Bethany has been baking the most delicous pies at her home.
            </p>
            <p>
                In 2013, we opened our first store in Brussels (Belgium)in a cosy little street
                near the Grand Market. People from all over the world fell in love with the soft
                cakes, heavenly cheese cakes, spicy apple pies... The store become a success in no time.
            </p>
            <p>
                In 2015, no less than 100 pies were sold every day and Bethany's Pie Shop moved into a large 
                building. After receiving many requests, it become clear that our next step was making it possible to order
                pies from the comfort of your own home from anywhere in the world. You are now looking at the 
                result of this: our very own online store, making it possible to order Bethany's delicious pies whenever you feel like
                it!
            </p>
